        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the veg is in the oven, boil half a kettle</p><p>Dice your<strong> tomato[es]</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>tomato paste</strong> in 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and add your<strong> chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) – this is your<strong> spicy tomato stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2930-Step-3-1644515170043-x200.jpg",
