            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the sauce thickens, combine your<strong> ground coriander</strong>, <strong>ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika</strong>, 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> on a plate – this is your <strong>smoky spice mix</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>meat-free chick'n </strong>to the <strong>smoky spice mix</strong> and mix together until they are fully coated, then tap off any excess spices  – this is your <strong>coated meat-free chick'n</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
