        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a separate large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated</strong> <strong>meat-free chick'n</strong> and cook for 6-7 min or until browned and cooked through – this is your <strong>smoky Spanish-style meat-free chick'n</strong></p>",
