        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>mayo</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic </strong>(not a big fan of raw garlic? Try using less!),<strong> </strong>1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]<strong> </span>cold water </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> in a small bowl – this is your <strong>aioli</strong></p>",
