    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>smoky Spanish-style meat-free chick'n</strong> with the <strong>crispy potatoes</strong> and <strong>roasted veg </strong>to the side</p><p>Top the crispy potatoes<strong> </strong>with the<strong> bravas sauce </strong>– this is your <strong>patatas bravas</strong></p><p>Drizzle the<strong> aioli</strong> all over the patatas bravas</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
